metadata.name: 555 Portal
metadata.description:
When the "555 Portal" opens, the energy moves forward and the the number 5, reminds us to eats the world. It invites us to launch ourselves into that adventure we so desire within ourselves.

Let go of judgments, free yourself from bondage and live life as if the world is going to end tomorrow.

If you are ready for the next adventure, I share with you the energetic explosion of this play to motivate you.
